 A mom of two has been arrested by the Nigeria Police Force for brutalizing and dehumanizing an underaged girl who lives with her as her maid. Although, it’s unclear where the incident occurred, a video obtained shows the woman being interrogated by police officers at a police station. ALSO READ: FBI indicts Nigerian big boy for allegedly defrauding U.S. university of $1.4million In the video, the woman was seen trying to defend why she locked up the minor and traveled out of town for nearly three days. The little girl’s entire body was covered with bruises and her face was swollen as a result of the severe beating she received from the suspect. 